### MongoDB Demo API - Custom Query Execution
### Base URL: http://localhost:3001

### Custom Query - Find All Users
POST http://localhost:3001/api/data/execute-custom
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "collection": "users",
  "operation": "find",
  "query": {}
}

###

### Custom Query - Find Active Companies
POST http://localhost:3001/api/data/execute-custom
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "collection": "companies",
  "operation": "find",
  "query": {
    "isActive": true
  }
}

###

### Custom Query - Count Technology Companies
POST http://localhost:3001/api/data/execute-custom
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "collection": "companies",
  "operation": "countDocuments",
  "query": {
    "industry": "Technology"
  }
}

