### Custom Query - Find Active Jobs with High Salary
POST http://localhost:3001/api/data/execute-custom
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "collection": "jobs",
  "operation": "find",
  "query": {
    "status": "Active",
    "salaryRange.min": { "$gte": 20000 }
  }
}

###

### Custom Query - Count Applications by Status
POST http://localhost:3001/api/data/execute-custom
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "collection": "applications",
  "operation": "aggregate",
  "query": [
    {
      "$group": {
        "_id": "$status",
        "count": { "$sum": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "$sort": { "count": -1 }
    }
  ]
}

